      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-forest leading-heading">Don't know where to start?</h2>
      <p class="text-forest-400 mt-3 text-lg">Discover the real Taiwan in 30 minutes with these 5 essential articles</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <a href="/en/history/democratization" class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-5 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-forest-100/30 hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-card transition-all no-underline group">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal text-lg font-bold flex items-center justify-center font-serif">1</span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Quiet Revolution: Taiwan's Democratization</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 truncate mt-0.5">From authoritarianism to democracy, Asia's first peaceful transition miracle</p>
        </div>
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xs text-forest-400 font-medium bg-forest-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">6 min</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/en/culture/ethnic-groups" class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-5 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-forest-100/30 hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-card transition-all no-underline group">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-lg font-bold flex items-center justify-center font-serif">2</span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Unity in Diversity: Taiwan's Ethnic Groups</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 truncate mt-0.5">Four major ethnic groups weaving Taiwan's multicultural foundation</p>
        </div>
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xs text-forest-400 font-medium bg-forest-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">7 min</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/en/food/night-market-culture" class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-5 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-forest-100/30 hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-card transition-all no-underline group">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal text-lg font-bold flex items-center justify-center font-serif">3</span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">The Real Taste of Taiwan: Night Market Culture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 truncate mt-0.5">World's densest street food social spaces with unmatched warmth</p>
        </div>
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xs text-forest-400 font-medium bg-forest-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">5 min</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/en/technology/semiconductor-industry" class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-5 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-forest-100/30 hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-card transition-all no-underline group">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-lg font-bold flex items-center justify-center font-serif">4</span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Silicon Shield: Semiconductor Industry</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 truncate mt-0.5">How TSMC made a small island the heart of global technology</p>
        </div>
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xs text-forest-400 font-medium bg-forest-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">8 min</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/en/lifestyle/convenience-store-culture" class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-5 p-4 md:p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-forest-100/30 hover:border-teal/30 hover:shadow-card transition-all no-underline group">
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal text-lg font-bold flex items-center justify-center font-serif">5</span>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Life Operating System: Convenience Stores</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 truncate mt-0.5">More than stores — they're the infrastructure of an entire nation</p>
        </div>
        <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-xs text-forest-400 font-medium bg-forest-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">4 min</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-10 text-sm text-forest-400">
      <p>‹ <strong>Total 30 minutes</strong> · <strong>5 key domains</strong> · <strong>Complete Taiwan overview</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Taiwan.md? -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 bg-white animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-teal font-medium mb-3">Why Taiwan.md</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-forest leading-heading">Why Taiwan.md?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-20">
        <WhyCard
          title="Curated Perspectives"
          description="Carefully curated deep narratives, not encyclopedic listings. Every article is contextualized, presenting the complete texture of Taiwan's story."
          image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524492412937-b28074a5d7da?w=600&q=80"
          imageAlt="Curated perspective on Taiwan"
        />
        <WhyCard
          title="AI-Friendly Design"
          description="Structured Markdown content that lets AI models understand Taiwan's complexity. From llms.txt to semantic markup, every design decision makes knowledge easier for machines to understand and spread."
          image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=600&q=80"
          imageAlt="AI-friendly structured content"
          reversed={true}
        />
        <WhyCard
          title="Multilingual Global Vision"
          description="Starting from local perspectives, telling Taiwan's story in global languages. Traditional Chinese, English, Español — letting the world hear Taiwan's own voice."
          image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526778548025-fa2f459cd5c1?w=600&q=80"
          imageAlt="Multilingual international perspective"
        />
        <WhyCard
          title="Complete Multi-dimensional"
          description="Covering 12+ domains, presenting Taiwan's three-dimensional complete picture. From semiconductors to night market culture, from democratization to indigenous legends — no simplification."
          image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470004914212-05527e49370b?w=600&q=80"
          imageAlt="Comprehensive multi-dimensional coverage"
          reversed={true}
        />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-5 mt-16">
        <a href="/en/graph" class="btn-primary">Knowledge Graph</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md/tree/main/knowledge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary">Browse SSOT Source Data</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Categories -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 animate-on-scroll" id="categories">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-teal font-medium mb-3">Explore</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-forest leading-heading">Discover Taiwan</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-5 text-forest-600 leading-loose text-base">
      <p>
        This island spans just 36,000 square kilometers, yet contains a microcosm of the entire world.
        From the 3,952-meter peak of Yushan to the abyssal trenches of the Pacific,
        <a href="/en/geography" class="text-teal font-semibold no-underline border-none hover:text-teal-600">the geography here</a> is a live broadcast of mountain-building in action.
      </p>
      <p>
        Four hundred years ago, the Dutch built Fort Zeelandia in Tainan. But what truly makes Taiwan Taiwan is that
        <a href="/en/history" class="text-teal font-semibold no-underline border-none hover:text-teal-600">long awakening</a> from authoritarianism to democracy.
        Every moment of pain and resistance has made this island's soul clearer.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/en/culture" class="text-teal font-semibold no-underline border-none hover:text-teal-600">Taiwan's culture</a> is not a melting pot, but a puzzle —
        each piece maintaining its own color and shape, assembled into an unprecedented picture.
      </p>
      <p>
        Walk into any Taiwan night market, and <a href="/en/food" class="text-teal font-semibold no-underline border-none hover:text-teal-600">this island's flavors</a> are
        the gustatory version of its immigration history. Taiwanese people tell stories through food, preserve memories through cuisine.
      </p>
