        TSMC's wafers are not just silicon chips, but proof of Taiwan's position in the global technology map.
        <a href="/en/technology" class="text-teal font-semibold no-underline border-none hover:text-teal-600">This tech island</a> has evolved from contract manufacturing to innovative R&D.
