        <p>Traditional Chinese is one of the world's oldest writing systems still in daily use, and Taiwan is the only major region globally that uses Traditional Chinese as its official script.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-forest-400 italic">
          Taiwan uses Traditional Chinese — the world's oldest writing system still in daily use,
          and Taiwan is its last major home. We believe our language and culture deserve to be seen and understood.
          Even if you can't read it, its beauty speaks for itself. This English version serves as a bridge
          to help the world discover Taiwan's richness. We also have a <a href="/" class="text-teal">中文版本</a>.
        </p>
